life_mission: Build scalable systems that shape the future
primary_strengths: Visionary leadership; strategic foresight; decisive authority
relationship_dynamics: Needs autonomy, respect, and aligned vision
premium_deep_dive: You are wired to see what does not yet exist and make it real. Your mind runs ahead of the present, mapping futures, risks, and structures simultaneously. When aligned, you become a gravitational leader—others orbit your clarity. When misaligned, you isolate, believing no one can keep pace. Mastery comes from delegation and trust. Your evolution requires learning that leadership scales through people, not personal endurance.

core_identity: Unifier of people around long-range vision
relationship_dynamics: Values shared purpose; avoids chaotic partners
premium_deep_dive: You govern through coherence rather than force. Your presence stabilizes rooms and aligns people toward common goals. Your challenge is allowing conflict to surface rather than smoothing it away. Growth comes from realizing disagreement refines leadership—it doesn’t weaken it.

You exist to rebuild what others abandon. Collapse does not scare you—it activates you. Your gift is redesigning life after failure. Your risk is disappearing into endless refinement. Evolution happens when you act before certainty.

core_identity: Translator of complex truth into human meaning
premium_deep_dive: You turn depth into language people can survive. You carry insight and emotion simultaneously, which makes you indispensable—and vulnerable. Your power stabilizes when you stop absorbing what you are meant to interpret.
